{"tid":2302013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"某個\"專業人士\"屌個17歲幫梓樂嘅FA","createTime":"2020-11-26T20:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T23:25:56.000Z","uid":308722,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f8798ee0d5524beda8d0a1981f16f087ae6520e8","tid":2302013,"uid":308722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T20:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WbQEqKj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWbQEqKj.png&h=00ecde4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單單打打，幫梓樂嘅FA仲要好聲好氣解釋，ANTHONY前一句dr曾，後一句想聽書，咁撚搶口啊嘛？咁撚臭串啊嘛？宜家就同你上堂啊，做咩道歉？放上咩大群討論下？上黎一齊討論下啦，討論區夠唔夠大？"},{"pid":"e3de6bfca3614ffe7bdb8608c86ad64f83f3cba5","tid":2302013,"uid":308722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T20:40:53.000Z","msg":"唔識引用回覆搞到變開po，sor"},{"pid":"d7bbaccecef16a6bbd7dc232bbe20b44b2353837","tid":2302013,"uid":54728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T20:43:28.000Z","msg":"似係博上位扮學霸 啲女女又濕晒"},{"pid":"0a18b33ddfe31ad4fe68677e780f65a051a258e7","tid":2302013,"uid":5459,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T20:50:36.000Z","msg":"阿anthony個story仲串人話冇做MRI就睇到ICP高添。ICP亦都唔係anthony所講用MRI就量度到架，要入OT擺條IVC駁住EVD先睇到架。<br />\n<br />\n同埋阿Anthony咁醒不如搵下咩係Cushing's traid? 唔使做MRI唔使駁EVD已經可以憑vital signs初步判斷到有increased ICP情況出現。<br />\n<br />\n如果阿Anthony知道咩係Monro-Kellie hypothesis，知道head injury嘅程度，就會明白assess head injury之後有冇ICP升係好平常嘅評估方向，而曾先生亦都冇提過所有head injury都係由ICP高引起。阿anthony你邏輯同知識都冇就唔好衝出嚟柒啦。"},{"pid":"8624d672ceec79d9aec66776abb106c502869110","tid":2302013,"uid":44869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T20:55:32.000Z","msg":"屌、以為邊個咁把炮<br />\n原來讀明愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1940a00cdd7d1d4643f1eeb94e12edf43acbfd","tid":2302013,"uid":38381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8624d672ceec79d9aec66776abb106c502869110","tid":2302013,"uid":44869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"cite